OL,3,CPost Office compensation still moving
OL,4,Cfar too slowly, MPs warn
OL,6,FPlans to compensate subpostmasters
OL,7,Fwronged by the Horizon IT scandal are
OL,8,F"still moving far too slowly", a
OL,9,Fcommittee of MPs has said.
OL,11,FThe Department of Business and Trade
OL,12,F(DBT) needs to "outline what more it
OL,13,Fwill do to ensure every affected
OL,14,Fpostmaster" is aware of their options
OL,15,Ffor redress, according to the public
OL,16,Faccounts committee.
OL,18,FThe government announced earlier this
OL,19,Fmonth that more than #1 billion has
OL,20,Fbeen paid out to subpostmasters across
OL,21,Fthe Horizon-related schemes.
