OL,3,CPost Office compensation still moving
OL,4,Cfar too slowly, MPs warn
OL,6,FBetween 1999 and 2015, more than 900
OL,7,Fsubpostmasters were prosecuted after
OL,8,Ffaulty Horizon accounting software
OL,9,Fmade it look as though money was
OL,10,Fmissing from their accounts. Many are
OL,11,Fstill awaiting compensation.
OL,13,FCommittee chair Sir Geoffrey Clifton-
OL,14,FBrown has described the scandal as
OL,15,F"one of the UK's worst ever
OL,16,Fmiscarriages of justice" as "thousands
OL,17,Fof people were failed deeply by the
OL,18,Fsystem".
