OL,3,CPost Office compensation still moving
OL,4,Cfar too slowly, MPs warn
OL,6,FReleasing the annual report into DBT
OL,7,Fand its accounts, Sir Geoffrey said:
OL,8,F"This Committee would have hoped to
OL,9,Fhave found government laser-focused on
OL,10,Fensuring all those eligible were fully
OL,11,Fand fairly compensated for what
OL,12,Fhappened.
OL,14,F"It is deeply dissatisfactory to find
OL,15,Fthese schemes still moving far too
OL,16,Fslowly, with no government plans to
OL,17,Ftrack down the majority of potential
OL,18,Fclaimants who may not yet be aware of
OL,19,Ftheir proper entitlements."
