OL,3,CPost Office compensation still moving
OL,4,Cfar too slowly, MPs warn
OL,6,FAccording to the findings of the
OL,7,Freport released on Wednesday, DBT does
OL,8,Fnot "yet have clarity" on the number
OL,9,Fof claims that could be submitted
OL,10,Funder the Horizon Shortfall scheme, or
OL,11,Fthe value of claims that could come
OL,12,Fforward under the convictions redress
OL,13,Fscheme.
OL,15,FAccording to figures released by the
OL,16,FDBT earlier in June, #559 million has
OL,17,Fbeen paid out to 6,337 claimants from
OL,18,Fthe Horizon shortfall scheme.
